      <h1>Perils of ignoring ICT developments in auto industry</h1>
      <h2></h2>
      <div class="info">
        <span class="info_l">
          By Ma Si | 
          China Daily |
          Updated: 2024-05-03 08:28
        </span>
        <span class="info_r">
          <a title="facebook" style="cursor:pointer; " target="_blank" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?title=Perils of ignoring ICT developments in auto industry&amp;u=https://www.chinadaily.com.cn/a/202405/03/WS66342fb1a31082fc043c51de.html"><img src="https://www.chinadaily.com.cn/image_e/2020/facebook.png" height="17px" /></a>
